---
title: Honey-Soy Glazed Chicken & Plant-Based Aioli with Sesame Fries & Japanese-Style Pear Salad
description: This magical meal is made in a flash but tastes like hours of effort went into it. The classic combination of honey and
soy speaks for itself, while sesame fries and Japanese dressing on a crisp salad add an extra twist.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/honey-soy-glazed-chicken-plant-based-aioli-004e4d4f.jpg
pdf: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipecards/card/honey-soy-glazed-chicken-plant-based-aioli-61725bb1fc819363c5542b03-cea2d313.pdf
source: https://www.hellofresh.co.nz/recipes/honey-soy-glazed-chicken-and-plant-based-aioli-61725bb1fc819363c5542b03
author: HelloFresh
servings: 2
time required: 30 minutes
nutrition:
  fat: 29 g
